column16: J.  D.   Martinez hits a grand slam (4) to left field.   Eugenio Suarez scores.    Rajai Davis scores.    Victor Martinez scores.

Rajai Davis singles on a ground ball to left fielder Alex Gordon.   Nick Castellanos scores.    Andrew Romine to 3rd.    Eugenio Suarez to 2nd.
Eugenio Suarez walks.   Andrew Romine to 2nd.
